data.description: NEW PRICE ALERT!!!!!! LOOK HERE THIS AMAZING OPPORTUNITY IS AWAITING FOR YOU!! Live in the perfect location with this 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom house in Skillman Forest! With its original 3 bedrooms and 2 bath, the added garage conversion provides an additional bedroom and ample space for your family. Don't miss this opportunity to live in the highly sought-after Skillman Forest neighborhood - come take a look for yourself today!
